A little script to download a complete Picasa web album.

Depends
-------
Python2.x
BeautifulSoup

Usage
-----
1. Run the script.  Optionally pass a --zip argument, if to create a zip archive
   of the pictures after download.
2. Enter the picasa web album url, when prompted.
3. Enter a directory path, where the images will be saved.

Motivation
----------
The Picasa application can do this.  But, this script is much more light-weight.
